00:07:42.503 --> 00:07:43.880
Bueno.

00:08:59.789 --> 00:09:00.915
Mi secreto es...

00:09:01.624 --> 00:09:03.501
que soy diferente a ti.

00:09:03.793 --> 00:09:06.546
Que soy una sirena.

00:09:07.255 --> 00:09:09.549
